            Ready to start something <span class="gradient-text">amazing?</span>
          </h3>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-primary/60 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
            Drop me a line and let's create something beautiful together. I typically respond within 24 hours.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
            <a 
              href="mailto:lardjemnassiba@gmail.com" 
              class="group relative inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 bg-primary text-white rounded-full overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/20 font-semibold text-lg hover:text-primary"
